# Inventarium
A menu-driven inventory system for a small business developed for csc4350, Software Engineering, at Georgia State University.

### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This automatic page generator is the easiest way to create beautiful pages for all of your projects. Author your page content here using GitHub Flavored Markdown, select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, to check out the new branch:


If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
